Class FXTextMenuItemSortingStrategy

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.drombler.acp.core.action.MenuItemSortingStrategy<MenuItem,org.drombler.acp.core.action.IdentityMenuItemSupplierFactory<MenuItem>>

    public class FXTextMenuItemSortingStrategy
extends org.drombler.acp.core.action.TextMenuItemSortingStrategy<MenuItem>
    A JavaFX specific extension of TextMenuItemSortingStrategy. This MenuItemSortingStrategy sorts the menu items depending on their text using a locale-sensitive comparison. This sorting strategy does not add any separators.
    Author:
    puce
